代表发言。巴勒斯坦常驻联合国观察员曼苏尔强调，巴勒斯坦是世界历史的重要组成部分，巴勒斯坦人民一直在坚定不移地追求其不可剥夺的权利，就像全世界所有其他寻求自决的公民一样。 联大决议不同于安理会决议，它不具有法律约束力。联大决议在一定程度上代表了国际社会的大多数意愿，具有道义力量。联合国压倒性高票通过！"},"attached_info":"CkAI2raZgqXJg84XEAMaCTExMDYyNTA4MSD9gq63BjAAOMMGQApyCTY2NzU2MjY0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6df91b3108aefbfd524b914989fe1d52_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1729347480.77529","card_id":"Q_1076881604","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1076881604,"title":"晁盖攻打曾头市时被毒箭射中，箭上刻有“史文恭”的名字，他到底是死于谁手？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1076881604","type":"question","created":1729077245,"answer_count":20,"follower_count":52,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[284,285,4364],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"晁盖攻打曾头市时被毒箭射中，箭上刻有“史文 恭”的名字，但疑点重重，晁盖是否真的死在史文恭手中无从得知。他到底是死于谁手？"},"attached_info":"CkAI2raZgqXJg84XEAMaCTExMTE5MjEzOSD9v764BjAAODRAC3IKMTA3Njg4MTYwNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"33 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4a04422db2238c47238c051d1ed902bf_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1729347480.77784","card_id":"Q_532940690","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":532940690,"title":"有什么画风很烂但是情节很有趣的漫画？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/532940690","type":"question","created":1652604424,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":96,"au