示范基地、皮洛遗址公园保护等重大项目。生态建设及环境保护项目7个、估算总投资72.8亿元，包括赤水河流域（古蔺段）综合治理、射洪城市生活污水处理及配套基础设施等重大项目。 成都要大规模拆迁？成都规自局：以官方为准，现在很多消息不太真实"},"attached_info":"CkEI2raZgqXJg84XEAMaCTExMTE4NjUwNyDJur24BjAAOLUFQBFyCjEwNDg1Njg0Njd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"3.4 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-76029fe6d397c4252b7b4bb40b0f27ee_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1729347480.80904","card_id":"Q_958119421","target":{"id":958119421,"title":"为什么每个公司都有摸鱼的员工，但是这类员工反而还混的不错？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/958119421","type":"question","created":1728984415,"answer_count":76,"follower_count":173,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1378357,1380277,3603950],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"每个公司几乎都有那么几个员工，比价清闲，本质工作没有多少，大部分时间就是在摸鱼，但是公司却还在用这个人！@摸鱼团"},"attached_info":"CkAI2raZgqXJg84XEAMaCTExMTE2ODI4NyDf6ri4BjAAOK0BQBJyCTk1ODExOTQyMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"3.2 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-3234c6d7f005ea39d6ab83798fc933de_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1729347480.81223","card_id":"Q_970722107","target":{"id":970722107,"title":"苹果拼音输入法为什么打不出「倒反天罡」(Dǎo fǎn tiān gāng)？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/970722107","type":"question","created":1728992781,"answer_count":87,"follower_count":212,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[24,2032476],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"CkAI2raZgqXJg84XEAMaCTExMTE3MDg0NSCNrLm4BjAAONQBQBNyCTk3MDcyMjEwN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"2.1 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false